* Coverage metric is generated using jacoco tool and it is integrated in the automatic build file build.xml.
* Mutation score metricis generated by MAJOR from build.xml. 
* To see the results go to the benchmark that you want to see its results and see the mutation score  under “ major reports” folder and coverage reports in “ coverage reports”. 

* Run: ant -packagehelp for the indivsual benchmark to see the tasks.
* "run-major.sh" is the script that runs the mutation analysis using MAJOR. It is located under each source folder.
* ant jacoco.report is the command to run the coverage calculation.
